graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    DSPO -->|container platform| K8s[OpenShift/Kubernetes 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|v1 pipeline execution| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|v2 workflow execution| Argo[Argo Workflows<br/>Latest]
    DSPO -->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager /<br/>service-serving-cert]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|API calls| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|user authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    DSPO -->|mTLS & network policies| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh]
    DSPO -->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator]

    %% External Storage Dependencies (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|production metadata| ExternalDB[MariaDB/MySQL<br/>10.3+]
    DSPO -.->|production artifacts| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>AWS/MinIO/etc.]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|UI management| DSPO
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|workflow execution| DSPO
    Workbenches[ODH Workbenches] -->|pipeline submission| DSPO
    ModelServing[Model Serving] -.->|automated deployment| DSPO

    %% Workflow Backends (conditional)
    DSPO -->|v1 backend| Tekton
    DSPO -->|v2 backend| Argo

    %% Built-in vs External (mutually exclusive)
    DSPO -->|dev/test storage| BuiltinDB[Built-in MariaDB]
    DSPO -->|dev/test artifacts| BuiltinMinio[Built-in Minio]

    %% Kubernetes API interactions
    K8s -->|API server| DSPO
    DSPO -->|watches CRDs| K8s

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px

    %% External Platform
    style K8s fill:#6c8ebf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Tekton fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Argo fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#9673a6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Internal ODH
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuth fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Workbenches fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelServing fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% External Services
    style ExternalDB fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Built-in Components
    style BuiltinDB fill:#708090,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style BuiltinMinio fill:#708090,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
